============================================
AXIOM ESPORTS SIMULATION GAME
Version 1.0.2 (Placeholder)
============================================

This placeholder file represents the game installer for:
- Axiom eSports Simulation Game
- A Windows desktop application for eSports franchise management
- Single-player offline gameplay
- Career mode with team management features

ACTUAL GAME FEATURES (When Released):
- Career Mode: Build from amateur to world champion
- Team Management: Hire staff, manage contracts
- Match Simulation: Real-time tactical gameplay
- Player Scouting: Discover and develop talent
- Economy System: Sponsorships and finances
- Draft System: Annual player drafts
- Offline Play: No internet required
- Achievement System: Unlock rewards

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
- OS: Windows 10/11 64-bit
- Processor: Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3
- Memory: 4 GB RAM (8 GB recommended)
- Graphics: Integrated (Dedicated recommended)
- Storage: 2 GB available space
- Internet: Not required (for updates only)

This is a placeholder file for demonstration purposes.
